    {
      "id": "SEC1",
      "type": "heading",
      "title": "Project Statement"
    },
    {
      "id": "SEC2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "ABC Electronics manufactures laptops, monitors and networking devices. The company distributes products from Hyderabad and Pune to regional distribution centers across South India. Transportation planning is currently manual, resulting in high freight costs, poor truck utilization and delayed deliveries. Management has decided to implement SAP S/4HANA Embedded Transportation Management to standardize transportation planning and improve logistics efficiency."
    },
